fields.name: DnsResolverOutboundEndpoints
fields.description: The reference to the DNS resolver outbound endpoints that are used to route DNS queries matching the forwarding rules in the ruleset to the target DNS servers.

fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: The current provisioning state of the DNS forwarding ruleset. This is a read-only property and any attempt to set this value will be ignored.

fields.name: ResourceGuid
fields.description: The resourceGuid for the DNS forwarding ruleset.
